{"title":"古剑山 Misc","uid":"38edb1db1c0abf89c3bbb2c730c65341","slug":"古剑山 Misc","date":"2023-12-26T07:01:09.904Z","updated":"2023-12-26T07:02:49.753Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/古剑山 Misc.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/6.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"Misc\"><a href=\"#Misc\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Misc\"></a>Misc</h2><h3 id=\"i-have-the-flag\"><a href=\"#i-have-the-flag\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"i have the flag\"></a>i have the flag</h3><p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208131607810.png\"></p>\n<p>附件得到js文件和html，分析js代码和前端代码的关系</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208131905062.png\"></p>\n<p>html中调用了checkToken函数</p>\n<p>js代码中的checkToken是这么写的</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208132018245.png\"></p>\n<p>但是直接进行校验明显不对</p>\n<p>发现ic是判断条件，需要跟踪寻找ic</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208132209608.png\"></p>\n<p>直接写脚本逆向即可</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">key1=[118, 108, 112, 115, 111, 104, 104, 103, 120, 52, 53, 54]</span><br><span class=\"line\">token=&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">for i in key1:</span><br><span class=\"line\">   token+=chr(i-3)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(token)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>得到：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">simpleedu123</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>放入前端进行校验</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208132607674.png\"></p>\n<p><strong>flag{muWn9NU0H6erBN&#x2F;w+C7HVg}</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"幸运饼干\"><a href=\"#幸运饼干\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"幸运饼干\"></a>幸运饼干</h3><p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208132729310.png\"></p>\n<p>得到两个文件，发现flag.zip被加密，且其中也有同样的hint.jpg，直接明文爆破</p>\n<p>将hint.jpg用bandzip进行压缩之后ARCHPR明文爆破</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208133048604.png\"></p>\n<p>解压出四个文件</p>\n<p>在admin.txt中对ntlm进行解码得到password：54231</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208133453442.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208133520532.png\"></p>\n<p>接着根据SID压缩包中的GUID文件，利用mimikatz获取到masterkey</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">dpapi::masterkey /in:&quot;master.key&quot; /sid:S-1-5-21-726299542-2485387390-1117163988-1001 /password:54231</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>这里的master.key文件就是SID压缩包中的文件</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208133724082.png\"></p>\n<p>得到key</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">7a4d2ffbb42d0a1ab46f0351260aef16cae699e03e9d6514b3bf10e2977c5d228fda4a48e39b7b8a06a443c39653c2a3c3656596e7edc84e1c9682511c8343ac</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>再利用key对Cookies进行chrome解密得到flag</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">dpapi::chrome /in:Cookies /masterkey: 7a4d2ffbb42d0a1ab46f0351260aef16cae699e03e9d6514b3bf10e2977c5d228fda4a48e39b7b8a06a443c39653c2a3c3656596e7edc84e1c9682511c8343ac /file:Cookies</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208133830546.png\"></p>\n<p><strong>flag{mimikatz_is_bravo_xzjc72}</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"数独\"><a href=\"#数独\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"数独\"></a>数独</h3><p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208134732690.png\"></p>\n<p>附件得到两张图片</p>\n<p>不知道算不算非预期，gaps算好size一把梭就好了</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">gaps --image=image.png --generations=40 --population=120 --size=70</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208134842612.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231208134921583.png\"></p>\n<p>按顺序拼接得到flag</p>\n<p><strong>flag{4e4d6c332b6fe62a63afe56171fd3725}</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"jpginside\"><a href=\"#jpginside\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"jpginside\"></a>jpginside</h3><p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231210104436420.png\"></p>\n<p>查看文件头发现是pyc文件，修改后缀进行反编译</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">store = [] #数据太长已省略</span><br><span class=\"line\">key = raw_input(&#x27;Please input the key:&#x27;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">with open(&#x27;excellent.jpg&#x27;, &#x27;wb&#x27;) as jpg:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for i in range(len(store)):</span><br><span class=\"line\">        jpg.write(chr(store[i] ^ ord(key[i % len(key)])))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>key[i %<br>len(key)]在前几位还是key[i]本身，可以根据异或反推出key：rotate1234!</p>\n<p>再根据key推回完整的jpg文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">store = [] #数据已省略</span><br><span class=\"line\">key = &#x27;rotate1234!&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">with open(&#x27;out.jpg&#x27;, &#x27;wb&#x27;) as jpg:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for i in range(len(store)):</span><br><span class=\"line\">        jpg.write(bytes([store[i] ^ ord(key[i % len(key)])]))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>发现文件末尾有zip文件，其中头部两字节被修改</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231210112208349.png\"></p>\n<p>改回504b手撕出来</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20231210112320787.png\"></p>\n<p>得到加密txt，密码就是key，得到</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jpek&#123;39i0jf49229fie5j33f02403hj953012&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>凯撒枚举偏移得到flag</p>\n<p><strong>flag{39e0fb49229bea5f33b02403df953012}</strong></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"Misci have the flag 附件得到js文件和html，分析js代码和前端代码的关系 html中调用了checkToken函数 js代码中的chec...","permalink":"/post/古剑山 Misc","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.9k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"MISC","slug":"MISC","count":17,"path":"api/categories/MISC.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"MISC","slug":"MISC","count":17,"path":"api/tags/MISC.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Misc</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#i-have-the-flag\"><span class=\"toc-text\">i have the flag</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B9%B8%E8%BF%90%E9%A5%BC%E5%B9%B2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">幸运饼干</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%95%B0%E7%8B%AC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">数独</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#jpginside\"><span class=\"toc-text\">jpginside</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"nnnpc","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/2.jpg","link":"/","description":"安全萌新","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"西湖论剑C0deX战队WP","uid":"6bb955f37944b8dc069388619eaffae8","slug":"西湖论剑C0deX战队WP","date":"2024-02-06T11:03:01.854Z","updated":"2024-02-06T12:34:12.128Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/西湖论剑C0deX战队WP.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/6.jpg","text":"西湖论剑C0deX战队WPMisc2024签到题","permalink":"/post/西湖论剑C0deX战队WP","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":24,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"MISC","slug":"MISC","count":17,"path":"api/categories/MISC.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"MISC","slug":"MISC","count":17,"path":"api/tags/MISC.json"}],"author":{"name":"nnnpc","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/2.jpg","link":"/","description":"安全萌新","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},"next_post":{"title":"安洵杯2023 Misc","uid":"c217568099e3bd13c9582e8429e28a85","slug":"安洵杯2023 Misc","date":"2023-12-26T06:57:12.099Z","updated":"2023-12-26T06:58:39.961Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/安洵杯2023 Misc.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/6.jpg","text":"安洵杯2023 MiscdacongのWindows题目描述是：好像什么重要的表被修改了，猜测是注册表文件被修改 刚开始利用vol2进行查看imageinfo的...","permalink":"/post/安洵杯2023 Misc","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.4k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"MISC","slug":"MISC","count":17,"path":"api/categor